OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBen Wallace to quit as     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdefence secretary at       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Freshuffle                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ben Wallace says he will step down as  
OL,6, defence secretary at the next Cabinet  
OL,7, reshuffle after four years in the job. 
OL,9,FHe told the Sunday Times he would not  
OL,10,Fstand at the next general election, but
OL,11,Fruled out leaving "prematurely" and    
OL,12,Ftriggering a by-election.              
OL,14,FMr Wallace has served as defence       
OL,15,Fsecretary under three prime ministers  
OL,16,Fand has played a high-profile role in  
OL,17,Fthe UK's response to the Ukraine war.  
OL,19,FSources told the BBC they expect the   
OL,20,Fnext reshuffle in September.           
